            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-1 font-medium text-sm tracking-wide uppercase">2020 - 2023</p>
            <h5 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black leading-tight">Deloitte Consulting USI</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold mb-2">Senior Analyst</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Led performance engineering for 100+ integrations and drove cost improvements saving 4+ FTE hours daily.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Executive Profile / Interests -->
    <div class="h-full glass-panel p-8 rounded-[30px] hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-black">
        Executive Profile
      </h3>
      <div class="py-4 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h5 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">
            Global Perspective
          </h5>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            International travel & cultural immersion; exploring diverse business environments.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h5 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">
            Strategic Recreation
          </h5>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Golf (Focus & Precision) & Aviation simulations; emphasizing long-horizon decision-making.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h5 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">
              Future Tech
            </h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Futurology, AI innovation & long-term human advancement concepts.
            </p>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
